					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1790" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C537&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1074&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1432&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=209%2C146&amp;ssl=1 209w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 近日美國一名動保志工分享了親身經歷，一隻流浪貓在被她接回家短短三小時內便開始分 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/14/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%af%e8%b2%8c%e7%9b%b8%ef%bc%81%e6%87%b7%e5%ad%95%e6%b5%81%e6%b5%aa%e6%af%8d%e8%b2%93%e7%ab%9f%e4%b8%80%e5%8f%a3%e6%b0%a3%e7%94%9f%e4%b8%8b%ef%bc%99%e9%9a%bb%e5%b0%8f/">貓咪不可貌相！懷孕流浪母貓竟一口氣生下９隻小貓 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1790" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C537&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1074&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1432&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=209%2C146&amp;ssl=1 209w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/mahdi-rezaei-7CpzdqR-1vU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>近日美國一名動保志工分享了親身經歷，一隻流浪貓在被她接回家短短三小時內便開始分娩，最終一共誕下9隻健康的小貓，讓志工和整個照護團隊驚呼連連，迅速引發網上熱議，也讓社會大眾對於流浪貓的議題再度掀起討論與關注。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，這名資深的貓咪動保志工多年來致力於救援和照護流浪貓，在不久前得知一隻即將臨盆的母貓急需庇護所生產，於是便立刻將牠接回家安置，並為流浪貓媽媽取名為「瑪姬（Maggie）」，希望日後能順利找到人收養。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="933" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-JYhw8TtoxTg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C933&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-226396" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-JYhw8TtoxTg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-JYhw8TtoxTg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C587&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-JYhw8TtoxTg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1174&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-JYhw8TtoxTg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1566&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-JYhw8TtoxTg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=191%2C146&amp;ssl=1 191w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-JYhw8TtoxTg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「瑪姬」一次生下9隻幼貓刷新了動保志工團隊的紀錄，所幸牠們的身體都相當健康<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>「瑪姬」的體型相當瘦弱，從外表看來孕肚也不明顯，讓志工評估可能還需數日才能生產，胎兒數預測為三胎，但沒想到僅過了不到三個小時，「瑪姬」突然進入了產程，一隻接著一隻地生下小貓，竟足足誕下9隻幼貓。&nbsp;</p>



<p>「瑪姬」的生產過程讓志工團隊們目瞪口呆，志工坦言從未見過如此密集且數量驚人的分娩情況，同時刷新了團隊多年從業以來最高的小貓誕生紀錄，所幸「瑪姬」與小貓的身體狀況都很健康，如今也已經健康成長並順利找到認養家庭。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/14/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%af%e8%b2%8c%e7%9b%b8%ef%bc%81%e6%87%b7%e5%ad%95%e6%b5%81%e6%b5%aa%e6%af%8d%e8%b2%93%e7%ab%9f%e4%b8%80%e5%8f%a3%e6%b0%a3%e7%94%9f%e4%b8%8b%ef%bc%99%e9%9a%bb%e5%b0%8f/">貓咪不可貌相！懷孕流浪母貓竟一口氣生下９隻小貓 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
