					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 最近國外有名飼主分享了鄰居貓咪的有趣行為引起網上熱議，他表示每天中午一到放飯時 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/14/%e8%82%9a%e5%ad%90%e9%a4%93%e5%88%b0%e6%a3%ae%e6%b0%a3%e6%b0%a3%ef%bc%9f%e9%84%b0%e5%b1%85%e8%b2%93%e6%af%8f%e5%88%b0%e4%b8%ad%e5%8d%88%e8%ae%8a%e9%9a%94%e7%aa%97%e9%96%8b%e7%bd%b5%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2/">肚子餓到森氣氣？鄰居貓每到中午變隔窗開罵讓網友笑翻 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/francis-painchaud-vSaiyYyS0cw-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>最近國外有名飼主分享了鄰居貓咪的有趣行為引起網上熱議，他表示每天中午一到放飯時間，鄰居家的貓咪就會準時出現在窗邊，露出咬牙切齒的模樣，對著自己擺臭臉甚至發出激烈叫聲，令他覺得相當好笑。&nbsp;</p>



<p>該名飼主表示，自己每天都會在固定時間餵食自家貓咪，而餵食地點恰巧靠近與鄰居相連的窗，鄰居家的貓咪又經常待在窗邊休息，這導致他們慢慢地產生了一種奇妙的連結。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="813" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samuel-gartmann-qQrsiSahpXE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C813&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-226398" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samuel-gartmann-qQrsiSahpXE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samuel-gartmann-qQrsiSahpXE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samuel-gartmann-qQrsiSahpXE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samuel-gartmann-qQrsiSahpXE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samuel-gartmann-qQrsiSahpXE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samuel-gartmann-qQrsiSahpXE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">鄰居家的貓咪每到中午時，就會準時出現在窗邊對著飼主開罵<br>(示意圖/Unsplash) </figcaption></figure>



<p>每當飼主拿起肉泥條準備餵食自家愛貓時，總是會在窗邊故意搖晃，試圖引起對方注意，這讓鄰居家的貓咪漸漸開始出現異常行為，從原本只是安靜地觀察，到最後露出極度不爽的表情，甚至頻頻發出尖銳喵叫，反應越來越激烈。&nbsp;</p>



<p>這樣日復一日的相處模式，讓鄰居家的貓咪每到中午就會準時出現在窗邊開罵，搞怪又有趣的行為迅速引起網友熱烈討論，不少人紛紛表示「貓咪好無辜」、「活該欠罵」、「飼主要小心，貓咪很記仇的」、「搞不好哪一天真的破窗」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/14/%e8%82%9a%e5%ad%90%e9%a4%93%e5%88%b0%e6%a3%ae%e6%b0%a3%e6%b0%a3%ef%bc%9f%e9%84%b0%e5%b1%85%e8%b2%93%e6%af%8f%e5%88%b0%e4%b8%ad%e5%8d%88%e8%ae%8a%e9%9a%94%e7%aa%97%e9%96%8b%e7%bd%b5%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2/">肚子餓到森氣氣？鄰居貓每到中午變隔窗開罵讓網友笑翻 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
