<figure class="aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="640" height="427" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-139.png?resize=640%2C427&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-225980" style="width:714px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-139.png?w=640&amp;ssl=1 640w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-139.png?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">貓咪能感知人類情緒，會用低頻喵叫或安靜陪伴回應主人的低落心情。圖:pixabay</figcaption></figure></div>


<p>別再覺得貓咪只是隨便喵喵叫了。那些看似隨機的叫聲，其實充滿細節與心思。牠們正在用自己能掌握的方式與你對話、表達情感。當你下一次聽見牠喵喵叫，不妨慢下腳步、仔細傾聽，說不定，你們的「溝通」比你想得還要深刻。</p>
